{"tid":2300144,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"歐央行暗示銀行明年起或可恢復派息","createTime":"2020-11-25T09:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T10:05:16.000Z","uid":284376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"27076f9767bbf3169985bf57c0474e3bef0f180b","tid":2300144,"uid":284376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"【信報財經新聞】歐洲央行執委會成員默施(Yves Mersch)暗示，歐羅區銀行或可在明年恢復派息。<br />\n默施接受英國《金融時報》訪問時表示，假若銀行能夠令監管機構信服其資產負債表，足以抵禦新冠疫情對經濟和金融的衝擊，那明年將開始取消對於銀行派發股息的禁令。<br />\n默施補充，今年之後繼續維持派息禁令將是非常困難，有法律上的不確定性，因執行機制是基於逐案處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/finance/article/625008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2Farticle%2F625008&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=b461c97e\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/finance/article/625008</a><br />\n<br />\n銀行股又要升到hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5221b3ba40d0d4d5ef7b9b6df4704d60224c1ce","tid":2300144,"uid":141065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:05:16.000Z","msg":"hsbc 60"}]}